org.eclipse.emf.compare

Interface FeatureMapChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Diff, EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FeatureMapChangeImpl, FeatureMapChangeSpec

    public interface FeatureMapChange
extends Diff
    A representation of the model object 'Feature Map Change'. This particular kind of difference will be used to describe changes within a multi-valued EFeatureMapEntry attribute.

    The following features are supported:

    • Attribute
    • Value

    Since:
    3.2
    See Also:
    ComparePackage.getFeatureMapChange()
